{
  "stem": "10698.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're Hitler's henchmen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they walked in, the first thing is school out for children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we had to turn in furs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even if it was a fur collar, you had to turn that in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We also had to turn in radios.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But being that radios were usually registered, because you paid, you know, monthly-- but we had a radio that was disconnected.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because my niece died, and we disconnected the, the radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they didn't have any, any, anything to show that we have a radio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we could listen to the radio for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war begin, it was a shock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I, I heard stories about the First World War, but, you know, you can't imagine something when you don't witness it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they started to bombard, and people were killed-- neighbors were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just-- it was impossible to, to, think of something as horrible as something like that, that people can come and kill people for nothing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the, during the day when they were bombing, we were trying to, to hide in cellars and, and places.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, I'm sorry to say, but in our street, there was a, a drug store.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not a drug store-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- because it was just, you know--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because it was only for medications and things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very friendly with those people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to hide us during the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- not Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the, that's the idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--hiding during the day in the very deep basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of people came to say, hey, you hiding Jews, and us, you don't let us in-- which-- that's when I started to-- I encountered-- I'll tell you about my my, my father that encountered something.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, that was an experience also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one time when we were hiding, my father figured that-- so we bought a, a padlock on the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, lock me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They'll see a padlock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when they started to come to pick up people into the trucks to take to the Umschlagplatz, my father said, they'll see a padlock.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They not going to figure that nobody's home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mom, my sister, my brother, her husband-- and we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we came up after the-- because we had a super, which was not Jewish, but the nicest guy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because you see, you cannot judge a whole people of some bad, of some bad things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he used to let us know when it's safe to come out from the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we came up, the, the Nazis took the door out from the hinges.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was by myself himself in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just didn't feel like sitting in the basement with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's when we lost our father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And don't ask me for the date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember the dates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, you have to stay in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they used to pick up people were dying in the streets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- and they, and they were picking them up from the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First they covered up with any paper they could get hold of and then were picking them up with a, with a cart to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when they started with the, with digging big, big, big holes and make a, a, a--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just throw everybody in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- at that time, I took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, there was no maid, so I tried cleaning, doing things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you see, there's always-- it's a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know-- I can only say-- and the worst thing, we had a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I finish the sentence?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The neighbor, she said-- she was a widow for long years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, oh, good, I'll wind up in the grave with, with man in it, as a joke.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they had already-- they were putting children, men, women in, in the big ditch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
